<p>Welcome to the home page of the Northwestern Networks Group! <a href="http://networks.cs.northwestern.edu/research.html">Here</a> is a 
summary of our current research projects. If you are interested in joining as a Ph.D. student, or collaborating on exciting new projects, 
please send an e-mail to akuzma@northwestern.edu. Note that
getting into the group is not easy, and getting out is even
harder <img src="./images/ssmiley.gif">. Northwestern undergraduates are more than welcome --- projects are always available.</p> 
